      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. What if the encroachment isn't from the building itself, but from something else, like an unmapped utility line or an informal secondary structure that's kind of just... sitting there on the edge of the property? If those types of \"unauthorized\" or odd elements are found during the survey, how does that impact the zoning review for the new grocery store?",
